    "We conducted the experiments on rule generation by manipulating the number of top N terms with the highest TF-IDF values which occupied the final list of keywords used in the ARM.",
    "Based on the experimentation results in [45] for selecting the most suitable algorithm for ARM using e-news articles, we applied the FP-Growth algorithm for ARM.",
